{"tid":2339114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［海外手足行動］Hong Kong Watch 羅哲斯為香港人24小時絕食抗議","createTime":"2020-12-24T11:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T04:36:23.000Z","uid":91721,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b9670cf6add6e778c64575b8f3883b0ce73dba77","tid":2339114,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"今日是平安夜，關注香港人權狀況的英國團體「香港監察（Hong Kong Watch）」主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）將展開為期24小時的快閃絕食抗議，聲援中國各地的良心犯和受迫害的人。他同時向中共總書記習近平以「在中共管治下受苦的人」為題發公開信，向中共及國際社會提出12大訴求，包括要求中共釋放壹傳媒集團主席黎智英等政治犯，促請國際正視中共政權威脅自由世界.....<br />\n<br />\n詳見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/YY65JMULFRFU3EYEM77XJSJSBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FYY65JMULFRFU3EYEM77XJSJSBU%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=b1cd5a37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FYY65JMULFRFU3EYEM77XJSJSBU%2F&h=1635b55f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/YY65JMULFRFU3EYEM77XJSJSBU/</a>"},{"pid":"e652e19e10bcd373992e31483ab2b51a34713408","tid":2339114,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"7651aaf06698d51c4131bfe0eb9ae0b83c7b1ffd","tid":2339114,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d23e6ebe8ed87d4946564c8474570db3fe7b160d","tid":2339114,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"support Mr Roger's, take care and Merry Christmas (cancelled by CCP China...)"},{"pid":"7ed393124220eb8ef9c10398f6715599b97d05eb","tid":2339114,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"幫手like,comment,retweet啦要<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1342070172312625154?s=19\" dat